" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/wactor_production_910inc_vtuber_accused_of_unfair_treatment_by_the_company.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/wactor_production_910inc_vtuber_accused_of_unfair_treatment_by_the_company.jpg" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/wactor_production_910inc_vtuber_accused_of_unfair_treatment_by_the_company.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-116081"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：X（推特）<br> © 2019 华克多有限公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>WACTOR Production是WACTOR株式会社运营的VTuber办事处，已扩展到日本、南美（西班牙语国家）、中国等地区，在南美特别受欢迎，但在2023年（令和） 5年）从2月左右开始，接连发现附属人才失踪和不公平待遇的情况。此外，在经纪公司宣布将公开人气艺人日南空的表演者/声优模特的个人信息并采取法律行动后，公司和经纪公司受到了严厉批评。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="QbPD5P6c6r"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/">针对附属VTuber活动的接连停止，WACTOR Productions应该面对的拉丁美洲观众和粉丝的声音</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“针对附属 VTuber 的活动连续停止，WACTOR Productions 应该面对拉丁美洲观众和粉丝的声音” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/embed/#?secret=Wn5HYtcrVI#?secret=QbPD5P6c6r" data-secret="QbPD5P6c6r" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="UXpkyinMmI"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-has-announced-that-it-will-disclose-the-personal-information-of-performer-and-voice-model-of-former-